<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fierce-adj">fierce <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɪəs/    美 /fɪrs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>凶猛的；猛烈的；激烈的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fierce animals
凶猛的动物</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fierce anger / heat 
狂怒/酷暑</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fierce competition</strong> 
激烈的竞争</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>fiercely /fɪəsli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>They look like the teeth of a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (凶猛的) animal.  （2010 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. fierce  </p></div>